      "type": "body",
      "section": "27.3.1.1.3",
      "text": "Net pressure coefficients, C_N, include contributions from top and bottom surfaces. All load cases shown for each roof angle shall be investigated. Plus and minus signs signify pressure acting toward and away from the top surface of the roof, respectively.",
